name: Better Swift Compatability
body: changed NSUInteger to int and fixed cocoapod update issues

name: Convert count to NSUInteger
body: decrementBy and setCount no longer allow negative numbers.  If there are any issues with this or anything is broken, please let me know [@cwRichardkim](https://twitter.com/cwRichardKim) or cwrichardkim@gmail.com

name: blank badge mode!
body: use [hideCount] to have a blank badge that still follows the same rules (hides when count < 1)
